text: Bhai tu to khud meri iitk life ka sabse bada memoir h, tere liye memoir me kya kya likhu mai! xD matlab campus me har ek activity maine jo ki, aisi koi chij hi nahi h, jisme minimum 1 badhiya memory teri na rahi ho;  chahe fest ho, padhayi ho, extra currics ho,  intern ho.. kuch bhi bhai! And seriously, jo bhi memories h na, use memoir me likhne ki zarurat hi nahi h kyuki mujhe pakka yakin h ki atleast mai to 10 saal baad bhi vo mere dil ka or teri ankho ka dard or chehre ki hasi kabhi nahi bhul paunga, jo ham clueless becharon ko complex ka endsem paper dekh ke aayi thi, naahi kabhi bhulunga vo intern ki rat se pahle wala CCD ka discussion, or fir uske agle din ka ek doosre ka whatsapp msg, na hi vo goa ke 5 din or na campus me spend kiya akhiri ka ek mahina, kuch bhi nahi bro.. I'll always remember ki we were there, in every success and failure, judging others, and watching tv series, saving each others asses in every fucking mth course!! Brother from another mother type ban gaya h bhai tu mera xD.. Definitely, Nous allons a Paris! <3 And haan, GS/ITC wale kitna bhi kaam karaye, Apna roz ka 1-1.5 hr ka RR rukna nhi chiye bkl kabhi, Offend hojaunga mai varna xD!! Stay Awesome forever bhai!!
